name: 10 SPECTACULAR CLOSE UP LANDINGS! Montreal (YUL) Runway 06R
description:
Thank you to RadarBox for supporting this plane spotting video! Find out more about them at https://www.radarbox.com/?referrer=AlexAviation

Montreal is the largest French-speaking city North America, and as such has a highly diverse international network, partly thanks to its home tenant, Air Canada. Watch some of these flights, plus a few domestic ones, touch down up close on runway 06R!

With thanks to  @Mark Brandon
